Package udel.GardenProject.plants

Contains the Plant class that stores all the information that can be obtained by the PlantLoader, and Comparators to sort the a list of Plant objects for searching. Distinct to other Comparators for PlotObject (singular) and other classes.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Team 0
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BloomTimeComparator
    Sort a list of plants by bloom time, assuming descending default.
    CanopyComparator
    Compare plants by Canopy level, by default descending.
    MoistureComparator
    Sort plants by Moisture, by default descending.
    Plant
    For every plant, there is a corresponding Plant object that contains as much information that can be loaded by PlantLoader.

    Plant data was gathered from public domain sources using Python scripts, and the plant data is stored as .json files in main.udel.plants.data
    PlantLoader
    Load all the plants from local file databases.
    PlantNameComparator
    Compare Plants by Latin or common names, sorting by common names from A to Z by default.
    SoilTypeComparator
    Sort plants by SoilType, by default pH descending.
